properties.name: 31st Street House
properties.description: Posted by Mildewproduction2524 N. 31st St springfield, OrI lived here from October, 1985-May, 1990. I would consider this my Oregon childhood home. My bedroom was the entire 2nd story. When we lived here there was a garden in the back, that is now another house. My sister\'s and I also had a two story fort that my dad built us, that is no longer here.
